Class MemFlags

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fs.starfarer.api.impl.campaign.ids.MemFlags

  • public class MemFlags
extends java.lang.Object
    Variable names for stuff stored in memory that: 1) Generally is used more than once in code, so it's convenient to track from here. These may or may not be used in rules.csv.

      • FLEET_SPECIAL_ACTION

        public static final java.lang.String FLEET_SPECIAL_ACTION
        Should only be used in conjunction with FLEET_BUSY. "busy" fleets will not be co-opted by MilitaryResponseScript, and FLEET_SPECIAL_ACTION is used to mark already "busy" fleets as being engaged in doing something specific so that they are not picked for a different action.
